  "title": "Office Administrator",
  "description": "<p><strong>Key Responsibilities</strong><br />- Create billing invoices and send them to customers<br />- Attend to daily emails from customers, act and reply promptly<br />- Assist with recording Accounts Payable / Receivable<br />- Other ad-hoc admin tasks when required<br />- Perform any other administrative duties assigned by the Management.​</p><p><strong>Requirements</strong><br /><strong>- </strong>1–2 years of office administration experience preferred; fresh candidates with good attitude may be considered<br />- Proficient in MS Office (Word, Excel, Outlook).<br />- Good communication skills, pleasant and service-oriented.<br />- Organised, responsible, and able to multi-task in a busy office environment.</p>",
